---
title: Gingery Chili-Lemon Chicken with Charred Veggies and Scallion Rice
description: Inspired by the Chinese-American classic, this lemon chicken recipe has bright and fiery flavours. Generously sauced chicken tenders team up with lightly charred veggies for a satisfying dinner any night of the week.
